abstractions of biomes as patches of tendrils and disks with palettes nodding to the 5 majors: tundra, forest, grassland, aquatic & desert.

[ 3 : save 6000x6000 png (slow) ]
[ 4 : save 8000x8000 png (quite slow) ]

objkt.name: PWTC #77

metadata.name: PWTC #77
metadata.description:
PWTC (Play with tubes and circles) is an artistic exercise of creation by repetition. Composed with only 2 simple shapes and a limited color palette, the beauty of the patterns generated comes from the repetition and random ordering made possible by the junction of artistic thought in intersection with code.

#Main Features

* ORIENTATION – 60% horizontal; 40% vertical
* TEXTURE – 50% point; 30% scribble; 20% scratch
* GREY SCALE – 5% chance
* INVERT – 2,5% chance

#Royalties split: 20% for minters.

* Minters in the first stage of DA will receive a printed version *

June 30, 2022

Generative Token by Eder Cruz + Morbeck for fxhash.

issuer.name: PWTC

objkt.name: Angular Variations (Holding Space) #147

metadata.name: Angular Variations (Holding Space) #147
metadata.description:
Angular Variations. Holding space for transitions. Once minted the lines maintain their design while the spaces between adjust to accommodate changes in canvas size.

There are no rarity attributes assigned to this artwork, its value is intended to be determined by viewer aesthetic alone.

This artwork was created using p5js.

linktr.ee/lisaorthstudio
twitter: @lisaorthstudio
